text: Embedded is a 2016 erotic political thriller film written and directed by Stephen Sewell and produced by Steve Jaggi, which sees a war correspondent meet an alluring, enigmatic woman at a cocktail party, before a dangerous power play engulfs the two. The film stars Nick Barkla, Laura Gordon, Ryan Harrison, Marcus Johnson and Peter Phelps. The film premiered at the Sydney Film Festival to generally positive reviews, with Variety calling it a "diamond like work", while The Iris called Embedded "a compelling watch." ==Cast== * Nick Barkla as Frank * Laura Gordon as Madeline * Peter Phelps as Cassidy * Ryan Harrison as Lance Corporal Jackson * Marcus Johnson as Porter * Rosie Lourde as Jade * Jak Wyld as Sergent Henderson ==References== ==External links== * Category:Australian erotic thriller films Category:2010s political thriller films Category:2016 films Category:2010s erotic thriller films
